        "share_text": "A fun little video @harryjayw & @zacheath and I (AKA @industrial_drive ) created for our good pals at \nPINTS & PILATES \u00f0\u009f\u008d\u00ba\u00f0\u009f\u00a7\u008e\u00f0\u009f\u008f\u00bd\u00e2\u0080\u008d\u00e2\u009e\u00a1\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00f0\u009f\u00a7\u008e\u00f0\u009f\u008f\u00be\u00e2\u0080\u008d\u00e2\u0099\u0080\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00e2\u0080\u008d\u00e2\u009e\u00a1\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00f0\u009f\u008d\u00bb\n\nPINTS & PILATES is taking over @theoak.tigheshill THIS SUNDAY! And we would love all of our friends to come. \n\nOn July 27th at 11am, the pub will be transformed into a pilates studio, with beers from @younghenrys and @heapsnormal on arrival, meat raffles, a pilates class expertly led by @gracemovementstudios, and wine from @verawineandbar.\n\nTickets are $30 with profits going to @inpiecestogether to provide training and support in the mental health and suicide space.\n\nSecure a spot at the link in @gracemovementstudios bio!\nEveryone is welcome!! \n\nVideo by @industrial_drive // give us a follow for more silly content \u00f0\u009f\u008e\u009e\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\u00f0\u009f\u0093\u00bd\u00ef\u00b8\u008f\n\nPs. Thanks for letting us be involved in your acting debuts \u00f0\u009f\u00ab\u00b6",
